title: Alec Baldwin Takes Donald Trump to the People’s Court During his Recording-Setting SNL Appearance
text:
Alec Baldwin Takes Donald Trump to the People’s Court During his Recording-Setting SNL Appearance Making history and throwing shade at the same time. by VH1 2h ago 
Alec Baldwin made his return to Saturday Night Live with more than just another hilarious dig at President Donald Trump . The veteran actor made history hosting the show for a record breaking 17th time.
